('5-MeO-DMT Safety and Tolerability Study', 'Phase I dose-escalation study assessing pharmacokinetics, safety profile, and subjective effects of synthetic 5-MeO-DMT in healthy volunteers.', 'University of California San Francisco', 'Dr. Alan Davis', '2025-08-01', '2026-12-31', 'planned', 'NCT05234567', 'https://clinicaltrials.gov/study/NCT05234567', true, NULL);
